哈喽大家好，这里是牧新，这个工作流是一个可以平替rask.AI & runway 实现文字识别翻译、语音语言转换、声音克隆、语音对口型等工作内容，适用于数字人制作、外贸视频语言转换等等场景。

具体的使用方法：

首先要在 Group 1 加载一个视频用于识别文字信息，然后要在 Group 2 加载一段音频 （8-12s）,用于音色的克隆。

由于音频无法自动进行保存和在工作流种进行传递，所以需要大家保存好 Group 2生成的音频（点击URL 然后再网页中进行保存），接下来将保存好的音频的路径信息粘贴到 Group 3的红色节点中，然后在下面的节点中加载需要进行调整的视频（可以是和Group 1 中的视频相同），最后点击生成就可以了。

关于工作流的视频教程：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1yT421r7to/?vd_source=6f74d739794605c324d3ff8af7cb7746

如果你有关于工作流的疑问和其他想法，可以随时联系我。

Hello everyone, this is Mu Xin. This workflow can serve as an alternative to Rask.AI & Runway, enabling tasks like text recognition and translation, speech-to-text conversion, voice cloning, lip-syncing, etc. It is suitable for creating digital humans, converting languages in foreign trade videos, and other scenarios.

Here's how to use it:

First, you need to load a video in Group 1 for text recognition. Then, in Group 2, load an audio clip (8-12 seconds) for voice cloning.

Since the audio cannot be automatically saved or transmitted within the workflow,so you need to save the audio generated in Group 2 (click the URL and save it on the web). Next, paste the path of the saved audio into the red node in Group 3, then load the video you want to adjust in the node below (it can be the same video as in Group 1). Finally, click generate.

For the video tutorial on the workflow:https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1yT421r7to/?vd_source=6f74d739794605c324d3ff8af7cb7746

If you have any questions or other ideas about the workflow, feel free to contact me.
